CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier, March 2, 1957, pg. A14 reads: "Beauticians Hold Tea - Beauticians' tea, held Suday [sic] at the North Side Elks, had this representative group among the participants. Left to right: Mrs. Alice Thompson, Mrs. Ann Penn, Councilman Paul F. Jones, Mrs. Catherine Green, Mrs. Mayotis Johnson and Mrs. Alexander Robinson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Alice Thompson, Ann Penn, Paul F. Jones, Catherine Green, Mayotis Johnson, and Mrs. Alexander Robinson, seated in North Side Elks for Beauty Shop Owners' Tea
